| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-0931 — Recovery Inhibition (dragonforce)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 84583383-b6a4-56f4-9bb2-83dbb9fcdd84"
index=* sourcetype=endpoint*
| where (CommandLine="*recoveryenabled no*" OR CommandLine="*bootstatuspolicy ignoreallfailures*") AND (process="*\bcdedit.exe")
